  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Ercolini e Savi's right in the centre of <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/tuscany/montecatini" title="Montecatini">Montecatini</a> and a great base for visiting nearby Tuscan towns like Lucca and Pisa or even the Cinque Terre. You're close to the shops and gelaterie, so you'll have the best of Montecatini Terme on your doorstep.</p>
<h2>Modern and homely</h2>
<p>The hotel's got a really fresh look and its modern meets traditional style feels homely. The staff are really friendly and will make you feel welcome and there are social areas around the hotel where you can relax and catch up after a day of sightseeing.</p>
<h2>Tuscan Food &amp; Wine</h2>
<p>The hotel's a la carte restaurant <em>La Pecora Nera</em> does fantastic Tuscan food (payable locally) and worth trying out if you want to stray from half-board one evening. They also have a wine list with about 250 different wines on it- this is not one to miss!</p>]]></description>
