  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Rooms </strong>are about 20m² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single bed).</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms </strong>are more spacious at about 25m² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single bed). These rooms have tea and coffee making facilities.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Bath or shower</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Air conditioning</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees &amp; taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tax of €3 per person per night is payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Sustainability Incentive</strong></p>
<p>Guests who don't request their room to be made up will receive a free drinks voucher</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
